{
  "$comment": [
    "Static masking rules applied by Neon (PostgreSQL Anonymizer) when the",
    "preview pipeline creates an anonymized branch from production.",
    "scripts/db/create-neon-branch.ts reads this, injects `database_name`",
    "from NEON_DATABASE_NAME, and POSTs it to /branch_anonymized.",
    "",
    "Two intents:",
    "  - REALISTIC fakes (anon.dummy_*) for fields where shape matters and",
    "    we want 'very real' preview data (emails, names, phones).",
    "  - HARD SCRUB (anon.partial(col,0,'redacted',0) → literal 'redacted')",
    "    for credentials/tokens/private storage paths — realism is NOT",
    "    wanted there; the value must be destroyed.",
    "",
    "We never mask FK columns (user_id, organization_id, customer_id,",
    "inviter_id) or primary keys, so Neon keeps referential integrity and",
    "the loyalty graph (cards/stamps/rewards) stays realistic.",
    "organization.name/slug are intentionally NOT masked (the franchise",
    "name 'T4 Diverplaza' is not PII and previews need it).",
    "",
    "Verify the anon.* function names against the PostgreSQL Anonymizer",
    "version your Neon project ships if a rule errors on apply."
  ],
  "rules": [
    { "schema": "public", "table": "user", "column": "email", "function": "anon.dummy_free_email()" },
    { "schema": "public", "table": "user", "column": "name", "function": "anon.dummy_name()" },
    { "schema": "public", "table": "user", "column": "phone_number", "function": "anon.dummy_phone_number()" },
    { "schema": "public", "table": "user", "column": "image", "function": "anon.partial(image,0,'redacted',0)" },

    { "schema": "public", "table": "customer", "column": "email", "function": "anon.dummy_free_email()" },
    { "schema": "public", "table": "customer", "column": "name", "function": "anon.dummy_name()" },
    { "schema": "public", "table": "customer", "column": "phone", "function": "anon.dummy_phone_number()" },

    { "schema": "public", "table": "session", "column": "token", "function": "anon.partial(token,0,'redacted',0)" },
    { "schema": "public", "table": "session", "column": "ip_address", "function": "anon.partial(ip_address,0,'0.0.0.0',0)" },
    { "schema": "public", "table": "session", "column": "user_agent", "function": "anon.partial(user_agent,0,'redacted',0)" },

    { "schema": "public", "table": "account", "column": "access_token", "function": "anon.partial(access_token,0,'redacted',0)" },
    { "schema": "public", "table": "account", "column": "refresh_token", "function": "anon.partial(refresh_token,0,'redacted',0)" },
    { "schema": "public", "table": "account", "column": "id_token", "function": "anon.partial(id_token,0,'redacted',0)" },
    { "schema": "public", "table": "account", "column": "password", "function": "anon.partial(password,0,'redacted',0)" },

    { "schema": "public", "table": "verification", "column": "identifier", "function": "anon.partial(identifier,0,'redacted',0)" },
    { "schema": "public", "table": "verification", "column": "value", "function": "anon.partial(value,0,'redacted',0)" },

    { "schema": "public", "table": "organization", "column": "logo", "function": "anon.partial(logo,0,'redacted',0)" },

    { "schema": "public", "table": "invitation", "column": "email", "function": "anon.dummy_free_email()" },

    { "schema": "public", "table": "push_token", "column": "token", "function": "anon.partial(token,0,'redacted',0)" },
    { "schema": "public", "table": "push_token", "column": "device_label", "function": "anon.partial(device_label,0,'redacted',0)" },

    { "schema": "public", "table": "sms_outbox", "column": "to", "function": "anon.dummy_phone_number()" },

    { "schema": "public", "table": "email_outbox", "column": "to", "function": "anon.dummy_free_email()" },
    { "schema": "public", "table": "email_outbox", "column": "cc", "function": "anon.dummy_free_email()" },
    { "schema": "public", "table": "email_outbox", "column": "bcc", "function": "anon.dummy_free_email()" },

    { "schema": "public", "table": "whatsapp_outbox", "column": "to", "function": "anon.dummy_phone_number()" },
    { "schema": "public", "table": "whatsapp_outbox", "column": "media_url", "function": "anon.partial(media_url,0,'redacted',0)" },

    { "schema": "public", "table": "push_outbox", "column": "device_token", "function": "anon.partial(device_token,0,'redacted',0)" }
  ]
}
